
Bollinger band wani indicators Wanda ya qunshi 
Upper band 
Middle band (simple moving average ) 
Lower band 
Bollinger band 
indicators ne dayake auna yanayi na Hawa da saukar farashi a kasuwa " Bollinger band suna sarrafa kansu bisa dukkan wani motsin ko yanayi da kasuwa take ciki 
Bollinger band sukan kusanci junansu (contraction) ko subude Subar jikin juna (expansion) lokacin da farashi yayi saurin  qasa ko sama (volatile)
Bollinger  Band overbought and oversold  
Bollinger band overbought  lokacin da kasuwa take bullish  ya kasance  price (candlestick ) suna bin jikin upper band batare  da taba lower band ba is considered overbought za'a samu reversal domin tabbatar da hakan sai ayi amfani da reversal pattern Kamar gravestone doji ,  shooting star, 
Bollinger band oversold lokacin da kasuwa take  bearish sai price (candlestick )  suna bin jikin lower band'  batare da taba middle band ba is considered oversold Kuma za'a samu reversal'  juyawar kasuwa zuwa sama domin tabbatarwa sai ayi amfani da candlestick pattern kamar  hammer,  dragon fly doji , 
Bollinger squeeze 
Candlestick  zai dinga bin tsakanin upper/middle/lower band suna matsewa  a waje guda batare da bawa juna tazaraba last two candle zai kasance sunyi tsawo Wanda tsayinsu zaisa Bollinger band budewa lower zai tafi qasa upper zai tafi sama middle Yana tafiya yanda yake ' anan abin dubawa idan candle din sama sukayi green candlestick akwai tashin kasuwa idan Kuma qasa sukayi red  candlestick  akwai saukar kasuwa
Bollinger band crossover 
A uptrend  market  candlestick suna tafiya tsakanin upper band da middle  band  sai su sauko su  ratsa middle band har yataba  lower band is considered reversal pattern to downtrend 
A dowtrend  market candlestick Yana tafiya tsakani lower band da middle sai yayi sama ya  ratsa middle band har yataba upper band is considered reversal Patten to uptrend 
Conclusion 
Yana da kyau ahada Bollinger band da price action ko da wani indicators kamar RSI ko macd domin tabbatar da aikinsa da Kuma trading Mai inganci 
